{"tid":328781,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"畢業後一直俾惡夢纏繞","createTime":"2017-07-20T00:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T00:05:10.000Z","uid":19923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b774cd25d77ed584a216291f5b88092fe57cc28","tid":328781,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣，畢左業幾年出後做左幾年野，仍然會夢見d好撚大壓力同驚既夢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我試過好多次發夢<br />\n1）唔記得第二日要考試，完全無溫過書唔知點算<br />\n2）溫錯科走左入去考試，一題都唔識<br />\n3）返緊工收到大學信話有一科唔計我credit要我飛返去讀過<br />\n4）過左個deadline先記得有份40%既功課唔記得左做<br />\n5）臨畢業先發覺有一科core無take到<br />\n<br />\n次次發呢d夢都嚇到醒，有幾次嚇醒之後半夢半醒咁好擔心係咪真係賴野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86018e3ffa958b6a716fea7eef3118cd6f1eea0a","tid":328781,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:31:29.000Z","msg":"好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6288f1a5d25d23cf77bc7f0174965b1bd6de3123","tid":328781,"uid