r />\n發夢都夢到做緊野<br />\n做極都做唔完<br />\n嗰時成日覺得心口有舊石壓住噉</blockquote><br />\n我琴晚都有咁既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240e42b5aae786f132e1c30b5ed0a072cd76a4d6","tid":328781,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:40:43.000Z","msg":"成日發夢比校長強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c7b60f9b120e047529521b1cb2f6d7e0e2eb85","tid":328781,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:40:57.000Z","msg":"發夢返工做錯野就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢返學既事通常都係夢見中學 返學校同朋友玩/吹水/日常野多<br />\n多數夢見中學都係因為夢見EX 想同佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac309be62fcdf04f85b677e5873d71c1051dcfc","tid":328781,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"其實好撚正 訓醒先知係夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻放鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f6166a391785222cc5a12b85ac01aa284db48a","tid":328781,"uid":74355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前有期狂OT<br />\n發夢都夢到做緊野<br />\n做極都做唔完<br />\n嗰時成日覺得心口有舊石壓住噉</blockquote><br />\n我琴晚都有咁既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情況持續嘅話<br />\n諗諗轉工/行啦"},{"pid":"b8b447f693beba673176d26e1c6c2642ff9e401d","tid":328781,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:46:33.000Z","msg":"仲有一年先grad，成日發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a476c3db2a81b3a529c76c400092cd92ae369367","tid":328781,"uid":128828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-